# 🍕 Pizza Order App

A simple Android application that allows users to place pizza orders with selectable options. This project was developed as part of an early-stage learning experience in native Android development using Kotlin.

---

## 📱 Features

- Select pizza flavors and quantities
- Submit an order and receive confirmation
- Simple and intuitive UI using XML layouts
- Includes unit tests to ensure application logic works as expected

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- **Kotlin** – Primary language for Android development
- **Android SDK** – Core Android components and APIs
- **XML Layouts** – For UI structure
- **JUnit** – For unit testing logic
- **Android Studio** – Development environment
- **Gradle (Kotlin DSL)** – Project build system

---

